── Constraint on ℓ from ΔN_eff bound ───────────────────────────────

  For the KK tower to be thermalised at T_dec, we need m_KK ~ 1/ℓ ~ T_dec.
  m_KK^(1) ≡ ħc / ℓ  →  ℓ = ħc / T_dec

  T_dec ~ 100 GeV  →  ℓ ~ 1.97e-18 m  (0.00 fm)

  T_dec ~ 150 MeV  →  ℓ ~ 1.32e-15 m  (1.3 fm)

